{"tid":1562104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何超瓊稱普通香港市民是違法暴力行為最大受害者","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:36:13.000Z","uid":314491,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3687cd37c0caa83f5c1d52896887416e61ed089","tid":1562104,"uid":314491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1480085_1_L_20190912003112.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1480085_1_L_20190912003112.jpg&h=33d12d3f&s={SIZE}\" />           信德集團行政主席何超瓊，以香港各界婦女聯合協進會主席身分，在日內瓦舉行的聯合國人權理事會會議上發言，講述香港的反修例示威。<br />\n<br />\n何超瓊說普通香港市民，是違法暴力行為的最大受害者，很多孩子離開家庭，成為全副武裝的暴亂分子，進行激進犯罪行為，令人擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n她又說香港各年齡層的孩子，在學校和網絡空間，被灌輸憎恨警察等思想，被動員進行大規模罷課，一些拒絕接受此類行為的孩子，尤其是警察的孩子，不管是在現實中還是在網絡上，會遭到惡意騷擾、恐嚇和欺凌，呼籲國際社會譴責有關組織者，和對孩子施加不良影響的人。"},{"pid":"1043b99e3a899e236d8f223e13de323176f2d852","tid":1562104,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9aefb68389c38114b75ce1389bd0516f9d43cb82","tid":1562104,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":